{"tid":1349946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國記者協會譴責暴力襲擊事件 明舉行靜默遊行","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:19:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1259d4c9f06e9857bf25e8503b1004047e69f0c5","tid":1349946,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"外國記者協會(FCC)發表聲明，譴責近日發生的暴力事件，尤其是元朗昨晚發生的暴力襲擊事件，導致有不少市民及記者受傷，並要求警方及當局盡快公正地處理上述暴力襲擊事件。<br />\n<br />\n會員將於明早9時30分在FCC外舉行靜默遊行，主旨為尊重新聞自由，反對暴力對待傳媒。協會亦將與香港記協會晤，討論未來保障傳媒採訪自由的行動。<br />\n<br />\n協會重申，政府應成立獨立調查委員會，以具透明度的方式調查自6月起發生衝突事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2197507/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2197507%2F&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKk8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=b7c0ee6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2197507/</a>"},{"pid":"ac65e1a0658ceafdf0ef739b3b51feb15010ecba","tid":1349946,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:36:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fcchk.org/fcc-statement-condemning-violence-in-hong-kong-including-against-journalists/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fcchk.org%2Ffcc-statement-condemning-violence-in-hong-kong-including-against-journalists%2F&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKk8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=4d2eddc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fcchk.org/fcc-statement-condemning-violence-in-hong-kong-including-against-journalists/</a>"},{"pid":"56faa8c381a6d01485d4472c30054a3b4482572b","tid":1349946,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}